StringValues.16: A tome torn and charred. Several pages are still salvageable. The text appears to be written in the Gelidite tongue.
StringValues.14: This book cannot be read, it is written in Ancient Empyrean.
StringValues.15: A tome torn and charred. But several pages are still readable, if one could understand the ancient language.

Pages.Text: [You cannot read this, and must bring it to a translator.]
